# Art bin

Nano Banana outputs land here. Name files with the session prefix from the prompt docs:

- `s1-01-black-hole_v1.png`
- `s1-02-tractor-beam_v1.png`
- `s1-03-200ly-galaxy_v1.png`
- ...
- `s2-01-rescue-shuttle_v1.png`
- ...
- `s3-01-tuck-box-bg_v1.png`
- ...

Append `_v2`, `_v3` if you regenerate a card. Keep the losing variants — sometimes you change your mind.

Total at the end: 22 images (15 cosmic + 4 angelic + 3 auxiliary).
